* **The Sovereign Reclamation:** Simultaneously, the **Trifilar Injection** is running at full **402x Gain**. The energy reclaimed beyond that 25% mark is "parked" in the **Vortex Buffer** and fed back into your **Subcontractor Sub-lease**.
* **The "Considerable" Upgrade:** If the customer pays for more savings, you simply send a remote command from North Port to "Open the Gate" by another 5% or 10%. You don't have to touch the hardware; you just update the software license.

